              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Pure (99.9%) boron target with 2.5 cm (diam.) and",
                " 0.32 cm (thick)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "FISCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Fission chamber with set of five 235U foils:",
                "- A thin foil with mass of 364 ug and areal density of",
                "  71.8 ug/cm2 enriched to 98.49% in 235U.",
                "- Other four foils with areal density of 478, 498, 513,",
                "  and 577ug/cm2 enriched to 93.3% in 235U.",
                "The fission chamber was placed 3.982 m away from the",
                " boron target and was completely encased in 0.66 mm Cd",
                " foil.",
                "The time of flight and pulse height from the fission",
                " chamber were recorded."
              ]
            }
          ],
